ActCanada National Parks Act
Department of Transport Act
SubjectRegulations Amending Certain Parks Canada Agency Regulations (Miscellaneous Program)
PrecisRegulations Amending CERTAIN PARKS CANADA AGENCY REGULATIONS (MISCELLANEOUS PROGRAM) in order to (1) harmonize terms used in the regulation with those used in the enabling statute and elsewhere within the same regulations; (2) correct grammatical errors; (3) align the French and English versions; (4) update obsolete references; and (5) add clarity to a regulatory provision.
